":223309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:18:37.000Z","msg":"我無嘢講"},{"pid":"8a61bc7377072bbee5007fc9936b23a8e3c1fdd2","tid":1322833,"uid":80725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:31:55.000Z","msg":"中共=中聯辦=港共=警犬維穩部隊<br />\n根本全部都係同一樣野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70149f4e28e70f5c3e0abb27ea4ae60fb705ce87","tid":1322833,"uid":80725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:33:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">提防顛覆</span></span><br />\n<br />\n遊行無用，勇武無用，連儂牆無用，民意開始逆轉，開始攰，好想死，仲唔散係弱智，仲唔衝係嘥氣，條例已經死亡，警察已經內鬨<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1320298\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1320298</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f122710def9fa4a3dca5e16f4b918bb29b620004","tid":1322833,"uid":4857,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:34:06.000Z","msg":"其實係咪係時候將7大訴求合一? 大家其實應該心知肚明, 只要有真正既普選, 就可以解決晒其他六大訴求, 係咪應該集中火力<br />\n1. 令大眾明白真普選先係最終出路(包括呼聲最高既追究警察濫權);<br />\n2. 要求政府重啟政改, 實現真普選"},{"pid":"3e49725a1fc912da31a1345431e72c7b996b81f2","tid":1322833,"uid":172465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:36:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7d7186522d255ef30a476413f21418a6dc832937","tid":1322833,"uid":276514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ef50f5550f6d5747ebfd3af03026ca5ec2a70cd","tid":1322833,"uid":264983,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T06:17:44.000Z","msg":"好有心機, 但你只打左個summary, 但跟住運動方向點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-16T07:03:01.000Z","msg":"對準政權，政權=政府+執法力量（警權），只要警權一被毀滅淋病就沒有話事權了<br />\n<br />\n講係咁講，想唔到執行細節<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}